{"tid":1183261,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個釘耳環，唇環，乜環都好嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-06-02T19:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T09:29:52.000Z","uid":252048,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e8c914bc502b6ccaf327daac20c1eeb856544e","tid":1183261,"uid":252048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"之前釘左耳骨 近排痴起條筋又走去釘<br />\n我覺得釘耳珠冇釘耳骨咁痛<br />\n加上耳骨個傷口好難好翻 成日都驚發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好佩服啲人釘肚釘嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a46fe9866196bf83c5f9b7b929d715c89510e26","tid":1183261,"uid":180323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:21:38.000Z","msg":"淨係釘耳環都驚到我死死吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直頭feel到佢枝針慢慢穿過我耳珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98548ab0bf1078baba7eb8dabcba3ce846ced369","tid":1183261,"uid":154255,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:27:15.000Z","msg":"閪環有冇人釘過"},{"pid":"d8a4938b15cd6293a0e989b1f2217712c3a9f84d","tid":1183261,"uid":26952,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5118e5c44d5544e665d6cdf06b354f49cc4f744","tid":1183261,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"上YouTube見到台灣有店<br />\n就咁用手拎支針穿耳<br />\n仲要支針鈍鈍地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴L線<br />\n用釘槍我都覺得危險"},{"pid":"9e1c3129e99ab412d77f926e6bdbd2735ba84f5f","tid":1183261,"uid":101253,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:30:00.000Z","msg":"我諗我一世都唔會試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d878172a174839faebf7cabfbaa95abf94dcb6ce","tid":1183261,"uid":238026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:42:34.000Z","msg":"我釘左鳩環 好撚爽"},{"pid":"dd6f6667e758a00d6110aec8ee01a398f5831844","tid":1183261,"uid":254886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:54:03.000Z","msg":"我都覺釘耳骨無釘耳珠咁痛<br />\n人手穿反而唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bedac40816808380fbf8ba945f046eaf96b0760","tid":1183261,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5118e5c44d5544e665d6cdf06b354f49cc4f744","tid":1183261,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"上YouTube見到台灣有店<br />\n就咁用手拎支針穿耳<br />\n仲要支針鈍鈍地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴L線<br />\n用釘槍我都覺得危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T20:03:11.000Z","msg":"英國都係咁 我覺得好過用槍"},{"pid":"aa814b9e8c16cbb67b5dc92ff4c3508d1dbda9dc","tid":1183261,"uid":21757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T20:32:28.000Z","msg":"大約5丶6歲時家姐去穿耳，穿完後想賺錢幫人穿耳<br />\n搵我做練習。一嚿薑丶一些生油丶一對耳環，替我穿咗耳<br />\n仲要做model示範比人睇，然後幫人穿耳收錢<br />\n<br />\n申：唔鍾意戴耳環"},{"pid":"aee371118da7b20046d3a93e0f343a3381b51fa1","tid":1183261,"uid":48165,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T22:08:48.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好撚驚釘耳窿 但完全唔驚紋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f0d84eef7f36b5db98c85454f83e29a3e57d94","tid":1183261,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T23:23:47.000Z","msg":"其實耳珠先最痛 得啲肉 釘嗰陣啲回彈力好勁<br />\n耳窩耳門耳骨都無咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唇同鼻都穿過 好享受痛嗰一刻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5df680940743782888c637560059ba7edd7992","tid":1183261,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:13:08.000Z","msg":"除咗耳仔，接受唔到有環喺身體其他地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef09d4d6bcb5acbf3fc420ee6ca84f934038063","tid":1183261,"uid":237844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"釘耳骨，狂發炎，夜晚頭髮一kick住就痛醒，狠心放棄後，傷口生肉芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4965808a93550cd538bff48171e022ac809251","tid":1183261,"uid":176121,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"細個仲讀緊幼稚園的時候隨口同呀媽講話要釘耳，佢即刻拉起我隻手就行<br />\n<br />\n我：媽咪，我地去邊呀？<br />\n媽：穿耳洞呀嘛！<br />\n我：吓，我講吓架炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住喊住口咁釘咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a345b227c88e6f54511413d1f7377d322d8d22c","tid":1183261,"uid":247478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"釘過脷環，完全唔痛"},{"pid":"c08b44b9d2fc88f5958f59c8bf9194f0e353118b","tid":1183261,"uid":252048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8a4938b15cd6293a0e989b1f2217712c3a9f84d","tid":1183261,"uid":26952,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"唔係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02115d76bf10ae5bacac6fb0e2d6c22e0ec3231e","tid":1183261,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a345b227c88e6f54511413d1f7377d322d8d22c","tid":1183261,"uid":247478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"釘過脷環，完全唔痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"含撚係咪好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c87a94476ebb223087e52fcb8d179166f42900d","tid":1